    <glossary>
    <definition id="def-00001"><term>acne vulgaris</term> <meaning>a skin condition in which skin pores and hair follicles become blocked, resulting in inflamed skin lesions</meaning></definition>
    <definition id="def-00002"><term>sebum</term> <meaning>an oily, lipid-based substance that lubricates the skin and hair</meaning></definition>
    </glossary>
